com.helger.jcodemodel

Class JAnnotationArrayMember

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.helger.jcodemodel.AbstractJAnnotationValue
      • com.helger.jcodemodel.AbstractJAnnotationValueOwned
        • com.helger.jcodemodel.JAnnotationArrayMember
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IJAnnotatable, IJGenerable, IJOwned

    public class JAnnotationArrayMember
extends AbstractJAnnotationValueOwned
implements IJAnnotatable
    Represents an arrays as annotation members

    This class implements IJAnnotatable to allow new annotations to be added as a member of the array.

    Author:
    Bhakti Mehta (bhakti.mehta@sun.com)
